@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style>
         body {
            background-color: #92ba92;
         }

         .about-us{
            background-color: #525e75;
         }

         .about-us h1{
            color: #f1ddbf;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 900;
         }

         .testimonials {
            padding: 0 20px;      
        }

        .testimonial-card .card-header {
          height: 120px;
          overflow: hidden;
          border-top-left-radius: 0.25rem;
          border-top-right-radius: 0.25rem;
        }
        
        .testimonial-card .image {
          width: 150px;
          height: 150px;
          margin-top: -60px;
          overflow: hidden;
          border: 3px solid #fff;
          border-radius: 50%;
        }
    </style>
    </head>
    <body>

    <div>
      <h1 class="text-center text-white p-5">About Us</h1>
      <p>
      <div class="container-fluid p-5 text-white text-center about-us">
        <h1>NemiVu Thai Restaurant</h1>
        <p>Established 10 years ago our aim is to bring home thai cooking to the homes of others. <br> We have passionate chefs who place pride in their use of organic and fresh produce in order to <br> create authentic, high quality dishes Our mission is to bring health and happiness through our food!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
       <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-10 col-xl-8 text-center">
          <h3 class="m-4">Testimonials</h3>
          <p class="mb-4 pb-2 mb-md-5 pb-md-0">
            See for yourself what some of our customers have to say...
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonials row text-center d-flex">
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-5 mb-0 d-flex align-items-stretch">
          <div class="card testimonial-card">
            <div class="card-header" style="background-color: #9d789b;"></div>
            <div class="image mx-auto bg-white">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1603208636390-4bce7c1d3846?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8" class="rounded-circle img-fluid" alt="testimonial-img-1" />
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h4 class="mb-4">Frank Jones</h4>
              <hr />
              <p class="dark-grey-text mt-4">
                <i class="fas fa-quote-left pe-2"></i>Best Pad Thai I ever had, can't wait to share this with my family and friends.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-5 mb-0 d-flex align-items-stretch">
          <div class="card testimonial-card">
            <div class="card-header" style="background-color: #7a81a8;"></div>
            <div class="image mx-auto bg-white">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8" class="rounded-circle img-fluid"  alt="testimonial-img-2" />
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h4 class="mb-4">Lisa Jameson</h4>
              <hr />
              <p class="dark-grey-text mt-4">
                <i class="fas fa-quote-left pe-2"></i>I lived in Thailand for over 10 years and this is true authentic Thai food!!
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-5 mb-0 d-flex align-items-stretch">
          <div class="card testimonial-card">
            <div class="card-header" style="background-color: #6d5b98;"></div>
            <div class="image mx-auto bg-white">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1647654034000-0010c45a569d?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2815&q=80" class="rounded-circle img-fluid"  alt="testimonial-img-3" />
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h4 class="mb-4">Tom Sarma</h4>
              <hr />
              <p class="dark-grey-text mt-4">
                <i class="fas fa-quote-left pe-2"></i>Always fresh ingredients - NemiVu Thai is our go to weekend treat and it never disapoints!
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
</body>
</html>